						               													<description>This game is played with two deck of cards in where one is the dungeon the other is the village. With a bag of dice the player must roll the dice and with the result gain certain amount of mana,cash,attack,and shields. After the rolls the player must decide to visit de village or go down in the dungeon to fight a monster (classical fantasy dingeon game yes I know). The game ends when 5 Clock cards are out of the decks and the player with more Prestige points wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;What makes this game unique is it exploits a dice pool of 21 dice and that the level system is based on a poker style achievements. You are allowed to carry 3 cards of each color.&amp;#10;Blue cards are Potions&amp;#10;Red cards are skills and spells&amp;#10;Green cards are Equipment&amp;#10;Yellow cards are Magical Time Artifacts (their power increases has the clock cards show up)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
